INSERT INTO `yl_article` VALUES ('18', 'IMAX Private Theatre Palais™私家影院·臻享', 'IMAX Private Theatre Palais™', '臻享阿拉伯', '', '', '', '', '', '/uploads/20170426/04128b8e4b51c90939ea4acf8ff7367c.jpg', ' ', 'IMAX Private Theatre Palais™私家影院·臻享为您和您\r\n的家人、朋友提供富有接触设计品味的至臻震撼私\r\n家观影体验。\r\n*适用空间：45-70平米', 'IMAX Private Theatre Palais™ brings the\r\nimmersive experience of IMAX® to medium-\r\nsized home entertainment spaces for close\r\nfamily and friends.\r\n* Space requirement: 70-45 sq.m', '阿拉伯描述', '1492656300', '1493273469', '0', '48', '1', '0', '/uploads/20170427/d1ceb275291a851cb372225abf29d6bd.pdf', '0', '0', '0', null, null, null, null);
